{"tid":2395902,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"護士私人IG留言「死黑警又嚟睇醫生」發佈資料被控不誠實使用電腦 嚴舜儀曾明言考慮判監 今判240小時社會服務令","createTime":"2021-02-05T08:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T18:17:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":220,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"b32c326542ebf17f4b9fc95144dcd00b05e55164","tid":2395902,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13477&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ER3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=7f75d4ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13477</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官<br />\n#網上言論 #判刑<br />\n<br />\n區(25)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：目的在於使其本人或他人不誠實地獲益而取用電腦、披露未經資料使用者同意而取得的個人資料<br />\n<br />\n上回裁決<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12853&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ER3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=ec02eade\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12853</a><br />\n上回判刑<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13318&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ER3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=7197f097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13318</a><br />\n<br />\n案情：被告為某一診所助理護士，在2019年8月13日中午，被告在其Instagram 賬戶發佈一張截圖，內容有一名警員(PW1)的個人資料：出生日期、姓名、身分證號碼和電話號碼，被另一名警員(PW2)發現，並通知PW1，PW1在下午去診所跟進，被告僱主(PW3)在得悉事件後，曾代表被告向PW3道歉，和承諾解僱被告。<br />\n<br />\n速報：兩項控罪分別判處‼️240小時社會服務令‼️同期執行<br />\n<br />\n（按：手足聞裁判官判刑時不禁落淚）"},{"pid":"650af218c903a947dbe3d03e157ea6f112fdfd7e","tid":2395902,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=